title: Bobby's BIG Music Announcement! + Lunchbox And Raymundo Pitch Business Ideas To Barbara Corcoran Of 'Shark Tank' + Bobby Surprises His Waiter
itunes:title: Bobby's BIG Music Announcement! + Lunchbox And Raymundo Pitch Business Ideas To Barbara Corcoran Of 'Shark Tank' + Bobby Surprises His Waiter
description:
Bobby announces the inaugural BobbyFest! Get all the details and tickets at BobbyBones.com. We talk to Barbara Corcoran from Shark Tank. She answers all of our job interview + money questions plus behind the scenes of Shark Tank. Lunchbox and Raymundo also get to pitch a couple of products to them. Bobby talks to Canaan Cox who he met at a restaurant after he gave him his number. Also, Amy talks about how she can’t figure out why one of her kids got a big check in the mail.
